title: #414: It's a RHONY Preview Episode, Okaaaay?
description:
"Real Housewives of New York" is so special to us that we just HAD to devote an entire episode to the new trailer. Join us as we dissect the preview one shot at a time (or at least as close as we can get). We had fun. Hope you do too.

Afterwards, Crappens Mailbag!!

See acast.com/privacy for privacy and opt-out information.
